Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就去下一條街那邊的偵查屋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we'll be in a scout hut down the next street.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心  我們不會在執勤時睡著的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't worry, we're not sleeping on the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午夜過后這里會非常冷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}After midnight it gets colder than a witch's tit in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,17號監控點就...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'OP17 in...'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-20號監控點就位  -收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- 'OP20 in position.' - Received.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:05:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}U2著名愛爾蘭搖滾樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:05:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道U2嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you know U2?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那個樂隊嗎  -對\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What, the band? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當然知道  你以為我有多老\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, course I do. How old d'you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小時候超級喜歡他們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was massively into them as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去過他們在溫布利舉辦的《約書亞之樹》巡演\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I saw them at Wembley on The Joshua Tree tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那張專輯很棒  我應該有一張黑膠版\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's a good album. I got it on vinyl somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  那你一定知道《射向藍天》這首歌了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right, so, you know the song, Bullet The Blue Sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-對  -我有件T恤上印著這歌的歌詞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yeah. - Well, I had this t-shirt with the lyrics printed on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是"我看不到那些戰斗機"那句\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, "I can see those fighter planes,"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面印的是一個怒吼女士的圖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}over a picture of a woman screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常喜歡那件衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was dead pleased with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很嚴肅  很有政治意義\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, it was serious, political.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  好過"弗蘭基說請放松"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. Not "Frankie says relax".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  也好過"選擇生活"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right. Not "Choose life".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但只要我穿那件衣服  我媽媽就會說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But whenever I wore it my mum would go,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"現在你能看到那些戰斗機了嗎  小內"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Can you see those fighter planes yet, Nev?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽們就這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's mums for you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:06:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么想起這個了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What made you think of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我確實沒見過一架戰斗機  所以也許...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I never did see any fighter planes, so maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在也有那種感覺  對嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You got that feeling now, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  我就那種感覺  老大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. Yeah, I do, guv.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是說...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...如果這樣不起作用  那...之后怎么辦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}..if this doesn't work, then... what then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他出現  我們就能抓到他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When he does show up, we've got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只要踏入監控范圍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He sets one foot on the plot
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會被被立刻...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and he'll stick out like a fucking...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人員  所有人員注意  6號監控點報告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All units, all units, from OP6, be aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一名男性  徒步從拉維妮婭花園走向莫頓大道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We have a male on foot, Lavinia Gardens towards Morton Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深色帽衫套頭  暫無更多描述  請待命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dark hoody worn up, no better description, stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他走進了拉維妮婭花園6號的私人車道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's entering the driveway of number six Lavinia Gardens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4號監控點  4號監控點  是否收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}OP4. OP4. Did you receive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4號監控點收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'OP4. Received.'
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待命  待命  他已經走到房子門前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stand by, stand by. He's down the side of a house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行動組待命  隨時準備行動\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'Mobiles standing by and ready to deploy.'
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可以看他怎么動手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We could be watching him work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別動手  我重復  不要動手  所有人待命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Negative, I repeat, negative, all units are to stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡  那是什么  手電筒嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shit. What's that, a torch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-要行動嗎  老大  -不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Should we make a move, guv? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  如果偽裝暴露  也就毀掉了整個行動\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, if we blow our cover, then we've blown the op.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再等一下  直到確定就是他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just wait till we're sure it's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警報解除  警報解除\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stand down, stand down,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一個年輕白人男性回家休息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it's a young white male going home to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他可真幸福  -6號監控點結束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- 'Lucky bastard.' - OP6 out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行動組撤退\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'Mobiles standing down.'
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累得我渾身僵硬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm stiff as a board!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.89,0:09:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不知道他們怎么每晚堅持下來的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know how they do it night after night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先  他們白天會睡覺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They sleep in the day, for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能晚點去上班嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can't you go in later?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要參加一個健康安全匯報會\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've got a Health and Safety briefing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前兩場我都缺席  上面提醒我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I missed the last two and it's been suggested from above
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最好關注這個方面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that I might want to start taking an interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-否則呢  -我不會讓他們有借口搶走我的任務\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Or what? - I'm not giving them any excuse to take my toys away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是在M25公路上身亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, you get killed on the M25,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.13,0:09:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們就是要去參加健康安全匯報會的人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they'll be the ones who need Health and Safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特派代表著領導力強而有力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, delegation's a hallmark of strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:09:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-而不是軟弱無能  -路易絲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- not weak, leadership. - Louise..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是把自己往絕路上逼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're running yourself into the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為內森不在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cos Nathan's away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想在你的工作和生活間\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's possible to care about your job
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到...怎么說  平衡  還是有可能的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and find... I don't know, balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-但我不行  -你認真試過嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Not for me. - How hard have you looked?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是這樣的人  一旦投入  不計安危\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's the way I am, in for a penny, in for a pound.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我羨慕那些能把工作就留在工作場所的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I envy people who can leave their work at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你才不羨慕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要遲到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're gonna be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是  過去這幾周觀察你...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's watching you these last weeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道一直很壓抑  緊張  殫精竭慮...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know it's been frustrating, nerve-wracking, exhausting...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不太確定...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm just not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不確定...是只因為要抓住這個人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm just not sure... it's just about catching this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What d'you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:10:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得你這么投入這個案子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think you're going at it this hard
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:11:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為你知道這是最后一次...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because you know it's the last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...而這個事實讓你前所未有的害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}..and you're dreading that more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就看看你自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, just look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你整晚在外挨凍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're out all night in the cold
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早還準備正常上班\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and straight back in this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都不想錯過  也不愿浪費時間睡覺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You don't want to miss a thing, or waste time sleeping,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你知道退休后心里會有多空虛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}cos you know how big a hole that's gonna leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不怪你  我怎么會怪你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I don't blame you. How could I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你最熟悉的事情  你就是這樣的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're in your element, it's just who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只希望當這些都結束  當你退休...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just hope when it's over, when you're done...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現有的生活能令你滿足  我能令你滿足\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that what we have is enough. That I'm enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也能滿足于酒吧小游戲和花園中心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you can make your peace with pub quizzes and garden centres.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前半句沒問題  后半句不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes to the former, no to the latter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  你又要拿這事取笑了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, go on, make a joke of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-除非被脅迫或者假裝可以  -科林\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Unless under duress or in disguise. - Colin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說得對\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很害怕接下來要發生什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am scared about what's next.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道工作  說真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The job's all I know and, to be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.61,0:12:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不敢想象退休后是什么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't even imagine what it's gonna be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好了  我得走了  -但我們會沒事  對嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Right, I'd better go. - We'll be all right, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I hope so.
