Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.25,0:25:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德爾羅伊·伊斯頓·格蘭特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Delroy Easton Grant.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.86,0:25:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從指揮延續性的角度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}From a continuity of command angle,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.14,0:25:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許由我繼續指揮到早上會更合理一些...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it probably makes sense for me to carry it on till morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.14,0:25:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高興那個高級調查官的課程沒有白上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good to see that SIO course wasn't wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.45,0:25:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  沒想到這么快我就用上了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'Yeah, didn't think I'd put it to use quite so soon.'
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.73,0:25:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮  內森  干得漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is great work, Nathan, it's great work.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.49,0:25:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你替我轉達給大家吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please pass that onto the others for me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.90,0:25:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我會的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.62,0:25:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我們八點見  -嗯  回頭見\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'll see you at eight. - 'Yeah. See you then.'
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.34,0:26:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和誰講這么久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.18,0:26:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們抓住他了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.62,0:26:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去把水燒上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll put the kettle on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.29,0:26:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-西蒙·摩根  -我是科林·薩頓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- 'Simon Morgan.' - It's Colin Sutton.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.90,0:26:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉這么早給你打電話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry to call you so early,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.14,0:26:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想親自告訴你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I wanted you to hear it from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.81,0:26:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來我們抓住他了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it looks like we've got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.74,0:26:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Simon?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.74,0:26:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我還在  老天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'Yeah, I'm still here. Fucking hell.'
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.62,0:26:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  我也是這么說的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, that's what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.38,0:27:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們位于拉維妮婭花園的一個監控點發現...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One of our OPs on Lavinia Gardens saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.73,0:27:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這就過來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'I'm on my way in.'
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.58,0:27:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  等你到了我把情況告訴你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}OK, I'll fill you in when you get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.94,0:27:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位我們老大  薩頓先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is the boss, Mr Sutton.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.38,0:27:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  長官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.22,0:27:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是幸會啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm so pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.10,0:27:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是要擊球還是投球啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So what are you, batting or bowling?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.14,0:27:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不太喜歡板球吧  長官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're not into cricket, are you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.66,0:27:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-喜歡啊  -但你還是不打吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yeah. - But you still don't play?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.42,0:27:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上我打  偶爾打  你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I do, as a matter of fact, yeah, occasionally. You?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.18,0:27:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打  我當然打了  擊球和投球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, yes, of course I do. Bat and bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.53,0:27:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真不錯啊  我的膝蓋不允許我投球了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, good for you. My knees won't let me bowl,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.22,0:27:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我還能像以往一樣地揮棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I can still swing a bat around as well as I ever could.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.01,0:27:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我  長官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, tell me, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.53,0:27:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得英格蘭在南非的機會怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}what do you think of England's chances in South Africa?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.14,0:28:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為我們可以再加一名快投手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think we could do with one more fast bowler
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.58,0:28:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我覺得我們有很大的機會\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but, er, I think we've got a great chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.34,0:28:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  我一直也這么說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, man, that's what I've been saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.01,0:28:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長官  得告訴你一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just so you're aware, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.58,0:28:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妻子患了多發性硬化癥  我是她主要的護工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}my wife suffers from MS and I'm her primary carer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.81,0:28:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很明顯  這會讓她受驚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Obviously, this'll come as a shock to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.22,0:28:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想會吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I imagine it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.70,0:28:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想確保她會受到照顧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I just want to make sure she's properly taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.74,0:28:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-否則我會很擔心  -抱歉打斷一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'll be worried otherwise. - Sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.77,0:28:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蘭特先生  請您簽署一下DNA取樣好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr Grant, could I have your signature for the DNA sample?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.65,0:28:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在去錄指紋吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Prints now, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.18,0:28:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.46,0:29:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-還用老式的方法呢  -對  還是濕定型好用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Still doing 'em old school? - Oh, yeah. Can't beat a wet set.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.46,0:29:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請把右手給我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I need your right hand, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.38,0:29:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白你為什么要費這個勁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't know why you're bothering,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.29,0:29:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們知道我總是戴著手套\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you know I always wore gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.10,0:29:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛你說了句很有意思的話啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That was an interesting comment you made just now
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.77,0:29:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關于總是戴著手套的那句話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}about always wearing gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.98,0:29:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們能取一個你的簽名嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Er, could we get a signature off you,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.30,0:29:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是確認你說了那句話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}just to confirm you made it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.53,0:30:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今晚是否接觸過\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you had any contact
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.57,0:30:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何體弱或年長的人  德爾羅伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with a vulnerable or an elderly person tonight, Delroy?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.65,0:30:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有一個屁股摔壞了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's no-one out there with a broken hip
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.01,0:30:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法拿到電話的人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who can't get to the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.25,0:30:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人需要幫助和注意嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No-one in need of help and attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.33,0:30:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今晚沒見任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I haven't visited anyone tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.61,0:30:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你有什么不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Very important that you ask
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.81,0:30:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請務必問清楚  德爾羅伊  好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if there's anything you don't understand, Delroy. OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.37,0:30:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-天吶  天吶  天吶  -怎么了  德爾羅伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Oh, dear, oh, dear, oh, dear. - What is it, Delroy?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.29,0:30:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們最好去調查一下我兒子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You really want to have a look at my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.65,0:30:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你兒子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.81,0:30:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這對我來說很難...非常難\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is hard for me... so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.77,0:30:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但鑒于這些罪名的嚴重性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}..but given the seriousness of the offences,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.96,0:30:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你們能抓對人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want to make sure you get the right man.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.96,0:30:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的DNA會跟我的一樣  或很類似\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}His DNA's gonna be the same as mine, or very similar,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.68,0:31:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外加我們身高一致  而且他住在附近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}plus we're the same height, and he lives in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.40,0:31:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什么直到現在才告訴我  德爾羅伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why did you wait until now to tell us this, Delroy?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.40,0:31:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我依然處于受驚狀態\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm still in a state of shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.09,0:31:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-胡扯  -對  當然是胡扯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Bullshit. - Yeah, course it's bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.01,0:31:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雙胞胎的DNA一樣  但父子不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Twins can share DNA, but not fathers and sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.20,0:31:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他說得對  仍然可能很相似\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's right, though, they can be very similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.29,0:31:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我們需要查這個嗎  -對  我們得打幾個電話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- We need to jump on this? - Yeah, we need to make some calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.37,0:31:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓帕特麗夏去查兒子  然后我們取樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get Patricia to look the son up and we can get a sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.92,0:31:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好  立刻去辦  老大  -并告訴她我一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yeah. Will do, boss. - And tell her I want to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.33,0:31:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可沒閑著\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You didn't hang about.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.89,0:31:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我們確定是他嗎  -我想是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- We're sure it's him? - Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.77,0:31:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-DNA會確認  -他在系統里嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- The DNA will confirm. - Was he in the system?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.61,0:31:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不知道  我直接來了這里  恭喜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}TBC - I came straight here. Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.96,0:31:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的大日子  你的案子破了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your day, your case,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.29,0:31:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我只是幫忙跨過了終點線  -謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I just helped it over the finish line. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.33,0:31:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我去看看團隊  -好  我也去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'll go check on the team. - Yeah, I'll join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.29,0:31:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我只想看看他的臉  -當然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I just wanna see his face. - Sure, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.40,0:32:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  所以他在系統里嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}OK, was he in the system or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.16,0:32:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-很復雜  -他沒開玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It's complicated. - He's not kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.09,0:32:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽完他們解釋后我不得不去躺會\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I had to go and have a lie down when they explained it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.25,0:32:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-只有你這樣  肯尼  -說吧  內森\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- That's just you, Kenny. - Go on, Nath.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.49,0:32:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,99年在布羅姆利有一起盜竊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's a burglary, back in '99 in Bromley.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.20,0:32:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地方警察通知了米恩斯泰德團隊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Local police inform the Minstead team,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.33,0:32:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他們認為不是米恩斯泰德犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but they don't think it's Minstead Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.13,0:32:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不符合標準嗎  -對\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Didn't fit the criteria? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.25,0:32:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以布羅姆利就自己調查了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So Bromley go ahead and investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.13,0:32:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受害者有一個鄰居看到一輛車\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now a neighbour of the victim sees a car
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.85,0:33:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她覺得有些可疑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that she thinks looks suspicious
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.68,0:33:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是就上報了車牌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and she reports the number.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.16,0:33:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們一查發現登記在德爾羅伊·格蘭特名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They run a trace and it's registered to a Delroy Grant
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.16,0:33:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地址是森林山\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}at an address in Forest Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.65,0:33:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們把他名字輸入全國警察數據庫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They put his name in the PNC.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.09,0:33:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果發現有六個名字一樣的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It IDs six people of that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.44,0:33:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個在哈克尼  有盜竊犯罪史  也登記了DNA\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One in Hackney, had a burglary conviction. DNA on file.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.65,0:33:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那這份樣本和我們的犯罪現場樣本呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right. And this sample was compared to our scenes?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.37,0:33:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們通知我們說哈克尼的德爾羅伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They informed us that Hackney Delroy
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.29,0:33:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是米恩斯泰德犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}wasn't Minstead Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.53,0:33:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-聽著很簡單  -對  只不過不知為何那份結果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Sounds straightforward. - Yeah, except somehow that result
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.53,0:33:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被登記到了森林山的德爾羅伊檔案名下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}became assigned to Forest Hill Delroy's profile
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.49,0:33:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并在我們的系統里建檔了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and a nominal was created on our system.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.96,0:33:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的錯誤成了我們的錯誤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Their mistake became our mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.65,0:33:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  而且還沒完\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. And it gets worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.05,0:33:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們隊里有個警員在去找森林山的德爾羅伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A DC from our team went to visit Forest Hill Delroy
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.09,0:33:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,調查他盜竊案當晚的行蹤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to check his movements on the night of the burglary.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.33,0:33:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  然后呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, and...?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.89,0:33:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他沒在家  結果也沒再繼續跟進了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He was out and it was never followed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.85,0:33:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那就是我們抓的德爾羅伊嗎  -對\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- And that's the Delroy we just nicked? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.09,0:34:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉到右側\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Turn to your right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.49,0:34:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果采樣了他的DNA\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If his DNA had been taken,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.65,0:34:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立馬就能鑒定出他是米恩斯泰德犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he would have instantly been identified as Minstead Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.89,0:34:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天吶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Christ...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.28,0:34:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那刻起  德爾羅伊·格蘭特這個人就被排除了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}From that moment on, the name Delroy Grant was ruled out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.45,0:34:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉向左側\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Turn to your left.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.93,0:34:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也沒在取樣名單上嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And he wasn't on the swabbing list?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.53,0:34:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  因為之前因DNA錯誤被排除了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, been formally eliminated by DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.32,0:34:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-所以就算用DNA取樣法你們也抓不住他  -對\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- So you'd never have got him that way anyway? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.20,0:34:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在2001年  德爾羅伊·格蘭特這個名字又出現\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In 2001, the name Delroy Grant cropped up again
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.61,0:34:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時有人撥打熱線  說他是嫌犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when someone called the hotline pushing him as a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.89,0:34:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在《犯罪調查》節目播出后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was after one of those Crimewatch appeals.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.41,0:34:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但沒有采取任何行動\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And the action got binned
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.68,0:34:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為犯罪數據庫說他測了DNA  被排除了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because HOLMES said he'd been cleared by DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.68,0:34:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.72,0:34:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.49,0:34:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自那以后有多少受害者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How many victims since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.57,0:35:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小德爾羅伊·格蘭特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'Delroy Grant Jr?'
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.24,0:35:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請進\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.65,0:35:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人跟你一起住這里嗎  德爾羅伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Does, er, anyone live here with you, Delroy?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.61,0:35:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我媽和我哥  什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My mum and my brother. What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.32,0:35:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒惹麻煩  也沒有人去世  不是這類事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're not in any trouble. No-one's died, it's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.01,0:35:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們有些不太好開口的消息要告訴你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But we do have some difficult news to share with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.53,0:35:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ok...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.97,0:35:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著  能坐下嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, can we sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.80,0:35:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽說過黑夜狩獵者的案子嗎  德爾羅伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you familiar with the Night Stalker case, Delroy?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.89,0:35:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-聽說過  襲擊老婦人的家伙  -對\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yeah, the bloke attacking old ladies? - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.28,0:35:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新聞上說你們逮捕了一個人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Said on the news you arrested someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.01,0:36:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We have, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.32,0:36:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很遺憾地通知你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm very sorry to tell you that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.09,0:36:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被逮捕的人是你父親  德爾羅伊·伊斯頓·格蘭特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that man is your father, Delroy Easton Grant.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.45,0:36:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.53,0:36:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能  絕對不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No way. It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.97,0:36:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.05,0:36:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們有多確認\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How sure are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.01,0:36:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還沒有百分百的確認\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, we don't have absolute confirmation yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.49,0:36:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果沒有極大把握  我們也不會來這里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but we wouldn't be here unless we were very sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.97,0:36:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟你父親多久見一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How often do you see your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.49,0:36:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.05,0:36:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們有很長一段時間與他沒有來往\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For a long time we had nothing to do with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.16,0:36:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我們"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"We"?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.72,0:36:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我媽  我哥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Me, Mum, my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.13,0:36:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.85,0:36:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在我還是小嬰兒時棄我們而去  我想是兩歲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, he walked out when I was a toddler. Two, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.89,0:37:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.45,0:37:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我8還是9歲才再次見到他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Didn't see him again till I was eight or nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.45,0:37:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天突然出現在學校門外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Turned up at the school gates one day
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.93,0:37:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答應要周末帶我和我哥去游泳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and promised to take me and my brother swimming at the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.89,0:37:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽不太樂意  但她看我們這么期待\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mum wasn't keen, but she saw how excited we were
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.85,0:37:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就改變了主意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and changed her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.28,0:37:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我高興壞了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was giddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.93,0:37:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像...圣誕節早晨的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Like a... kid on Christmas morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.93,0:37:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很早就收拾好了的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Had my bags packed hours before
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.51,0:37:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比他預定來接我的時間提前好幾個小時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he was supposed to pick me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.20,0:37:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得自己很想向他展示我的后空翻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I remember I really wanted to show him my backflip.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.93,0:37:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可悲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pathetic, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.93,0:37:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他沒來嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But he never turned up?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.04,0:37:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直沒再見到他  直到我二十多歲  而且\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't see him again till I was in my 20s and...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.41,0:38:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時我已經知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}by then I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.93,0:38:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-知道什么  -他對我媽干的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Knew...? - What he'd done to Mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.13,0:38:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴力  毆打\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The violence. The beatings.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.97,0:38:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他讓她經歷的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What he'd put her through.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.89,0:38:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些可憐的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Those poor women...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.61,0:38:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰先聯系誰的  你還是你爸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who got back in touch, you or your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.53,0:38:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.93,0:38:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和我哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Me and my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.49,0:38:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人告訴我們他再婚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Someone told us that he'd remarried.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.53,0:38:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他妻子有多發性硬化癥  說他是個完美的丈夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That his wife had MS and what an amazing husband he was,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.97,0:38:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個體貼的看護\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}what an amazing carer...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.05,0:38:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你肯定難以相信吧  -對\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- That must've been difficult to believe? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.24,0:38:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想著"我得親眼看看"  所以我們去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"This I have to see," I thought. So we go round.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.65,0:38:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"好啊  爸  好久不見"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Hello, Dad. Long time, no see."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.61,0:38:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All true.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.57,0:38:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的妻子人很好  但她需要很多照顧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}His wife was sweet, but she needed a lot of care...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.72,0:38:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他在那  細心地照顧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and there he was, providing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.97,0:39:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,體貼  耐心  井井有條\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kind, patient, everything organised.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.61,0:39:06.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不嫉妒她  我怎么能呢  但我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't begrudge her, how could I? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.13,0:39:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看著很難受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hard to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.80,0:39:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還要告訴你些其他事  德爾羅伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Something else we need to tell you, Delroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.68,0:39:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們完全不相信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're giving it no credit whatsoever
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.89,0:39:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你父親稱是你犯下了那些罪行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but your father has accused you of committing these crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.45,0:39:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么  -對\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What...? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.49,0:39:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像帕特麗夏說的  我們完全不信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As Patricia said, we don't believe it for a minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.53,0:39:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們必須通過DNA測試排除你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but, er, we will have to eliminate you with a DNA test.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.65,0:39:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  等等  他說.\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sorry, hang on, he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.89,0:39:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強奸和那一切  他說都是我干的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The rapes and everything? He said it was me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.76,0:39:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他為什么要這么說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why would he say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.85,0:39:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他就是這種人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Because that's the sort of person he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.93,0:39:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且從你剛才告訴我們的來看  他一直是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and, from what you're telling us, always was.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.13,0:40:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-給你  -謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- There you go. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.32,0:40:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們沒有鱷梨泥  我給你買了火腿芝士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They didn't have any torn avocado, I got you ham and cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.61,0:40:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.53,0:40:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我奶奶92歲了依然染發  所剩無幾的頭發\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My nan's 92 and still dyes her hair... what's left of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.97,0:40:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說當你變老后  似乎就失去了身份\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She said when you get old it's like you lose your identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.76,0:40:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們看不見你  只看到一個老人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}People don't see you, they just see an old person -
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.68,0:40:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白頭發  淺色大衣  老花鏡  羊群中的一只\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}grey hair, fawn coat, bad glasses, a sheep in a flock.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.24,0:40:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以這案子這么久都沒破  隱形的受害者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's why this went on so long. Victims were invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.65,0:40:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  但我們其他人卻不承認\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, and the rest of us are in denial.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.37,0:40:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都認為不會發生在自己身上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We all think it won't happen to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.76,0:40:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們能逆勢而行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll buck the trend.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.57,0:40:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便盆  假牙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bedpans, false teeth,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.80,0:40:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,癡呆  助行架  不可能  不必了  我們不會\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}dementia, Zimmer frame. No way, no thanks. Not us, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.93,0:40:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我們助長謊言的方式是忽略他們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And the way we feed that lie is to ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.65,0:40:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們注意到他們  但卻視而不見\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, we notice them, but we don't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.24,0:41:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不會避開視線  但也絕不會多看一眼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We don't avert our gaze, but we certainly don't linger
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.57,0:41:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他們是我們不想要卻逃不過的未來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}cos they're the future we don't want and can't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.24,0:41:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  就像我們在責備他們一般  對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. It's like we blame them, innit.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.72,0:41:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.93,0:41:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這說明了我們是怎么樣的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And what the fuck does that say about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.72,0:41:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.24,0:41:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說當這一切結束  會給我重創\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You said when this was over it would hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.68,0:41:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我說過  來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I did. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.05,0:41:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好消息嗎  -DNA結果剛出來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Good news? - Just got the DNA back -
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.57,0:41:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既成事實  與我們的所有樣本都百分百匹配\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}effectively 100% match with all our samples.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.76,0:41:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強奸案的精液\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Semen from the rapes,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.68,0:41:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈尼斯街受害者面部的口水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}saliva from the cheek of the Harness Street victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.28,0:41:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-科爾布里奇路的橙汁盒  -"既成事實"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- the orange juice carton at Colbridge Road... - "Effectively"?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.49,0:41:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是這樣措辭的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, they word it like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.85,0:41:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"德爾羅伊·格蘭特的DNA\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"The DNA taken from Delroy Grant
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.16,0:41:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與其他人相比  有47.5的10的24次方倍幾率\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"is 47.5 septillion times more likely to be linked to the DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.05,0:41:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與米恩斯泰德犯相關"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"of Minstead Man than an unrelated person."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.24,0:42:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"10的24次方"  我喜歡這說法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Septillion." I like the sound of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.76,0:42:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那螺絲刀的痕跡呢  -絕對是他的  老大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What about the screwdriver marks? - Definitely his, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.80,0:42:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們在搜查到DNA的兩個現場看到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As they're present at two of the scenes where we got DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.32,0:42:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有其他沒有DNA的現場也有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and loads of scenes where we didn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.89,0:42:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這將他與其他數起案件聯系在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it links him to literally dozens of offences.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.65,0:42:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經告知他這一切了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Has he been confronted with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.32,0:42:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們開始砸證據后  他就一言不發\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No commented as soon as we started rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.45,0:42:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇家檢察署給了我們時間\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}CPS have given us a slot.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.24,0:42:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得應該盡可能多的起訴他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I say we charge him with as much as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.49,0:42:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管什么"反正他肯定要坐牢了"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}never mind "He's going down already."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.72,0:42:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我同意  我們要為盡量多的受害者伸張正義\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Agreed. We get justice for as many victims as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.24,0:42:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們從嚴處置他吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's throw the fucking book at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.89,0:42:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你理解今天對你提起的這些指控嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you understand the charges brought against you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.76,0:42:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我理解  -你怎么辯護\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yeah, I do. - And how do you plead?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.57,0:42:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.41,0:42:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蘭特先生  你被起訴犯下22起罪行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr Grant, you are charged with 22 offences
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.93,0:42:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}格林威奇地方法庭
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.93,0:42:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且都是重罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of the utmost gravity,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.16,0:42:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五起強奸罪  六起猥褻罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}five of rape, six indecent assaults,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.93,0:42:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和11起盜竊罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and 11 burglaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.20,0:42:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡管你拒絕認罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Notwithstanding that you deny them,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.05,0:43:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在我們看來  如果被判有罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}there is, in our opinion, a very high likelihood
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.13,0:43:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很有可能會被判很長的牢獄之刑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that, if convicted, you may well receive a long prison sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.13,0:43:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你將還押候審  待在...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You are remanded in custody to...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.80,0:43:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝爾瑪什  女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Belmarsh, Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.57,0:43:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝爾瑪什監獄\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}To HMP Belmarsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.89,0:43:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在很多警察都過了退休年齡后繼續工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Plenty of officers working past retirement age now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.24,0:43:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但人總有退休的一天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everybody's got to go sometime, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.85,0:43:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是說說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.80,0:43:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基爾伯恩的督察已經退休后繼續工作五年了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}DI up in Kilburn got his bus pass five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.41,0:43:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-五年  -對\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Five years? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.93,0:43:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前兩天還破了一樁雙殺案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Closed a double murder the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.97,0:44:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想走  我可以收拾這里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can finish up here if you want to get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.76,0:44:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  你回去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, no. You're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.28,0:44:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你確定嗎  -嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You sure? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.68,0:44:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好  -內森\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Right. - Nathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.28,0:44:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.24,0:44:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你接受了我  當其他人都不怎么情愿的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You let me in when, er, the others weren't so inclined.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.68,0:44:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感激\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.85,0:44:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝天謝地我這么做了  老大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank fuck I did, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.61,0:45:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}2011年3月德爾羅伊·格蘭特被判在17年間\N總共29項罪名成立  包括強奸和性侵
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.24,0:45:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}他被判最低二十七年監禁
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.01,0:45:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}本劇為紀念他的所有受害者
